        RandomSearch - Inference. This is like Simulated Annealing without temperature.
        Parameters:
        h[] - a population of classifier chains
        h_w[] - weights associated with h[]
        x - the Instance to perform inference on (i.e, p(y|x))
        T - number of iterations
        r - random number generator
        y0[] - initial guess for y
        Returns:
        the classification y
